          en: "Man 2 is kind, thoughtful and always willing to adjust and help. He lacks self-confidence and is also suspicious and jealous. Woman 3 is imaginative, versatile, talented and lively and she has social awareness. Both will start on a harmonious note and their intentions are good. But as time goes on, woman 3 will find that he is too shy and not suitable for her. While man 2 will find her out of his league, proud, independent, and will surely suspect her of having an extramarital affair. And woman 3 has nothing to lose by bearing the accusation. The relationship is unlikely to last long.",
